{"tid":38532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"係學校飲jolly sandy比人記小過","createTime":"2016-12-14T03:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T13:11:56.000Z","uid":36497,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edb2068cf089dacf758bec063238648f593a9794","tid":38532,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:45:16.000Z","msg":"大家都知 , jolly sandy 係一種得0.5%酒精o既飲品 <br />\r\n今日我o係lunch time 果時買左罐 jolly sandy黎飲 (做緊特價3蚊一罐)<br />\r\n點知俾我間學校d老師見到 <br />\r\n起初我覺得無咩野 , 因為 jolly sandy 可以o係7仔 , ok 果d買到(即使唔夠18 , 著緊校服) <br />\r\n點知 一入到學校 , 訓導就黎搵我 <br />\r\n話我著住校服o係街上飲酒 , 影響校譽 <br />\r\n搞到好大鑊 <br />\r\n唔止記缺點 , 仲記埋小過 而家仲要見埋我家長 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我...應該點做?<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56b93d700446f72933349cb65e7987b382af268a","tid":38532,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"架陣啲六七十後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223b062165eca37e2cf0aa0d43d8b0b440947589","tid":38532,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"頭香"},{"pid":"c0a388967049fdd1b09591f161a14e5144e17ff1","tid":38532,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"個老師係90後？"},{"pid":"505c7706c7cd1d9f65c8468f08fea4475e483495","tid":38532,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭香</blockquote><br />\n(笑"},{"pid":"4258d051c959abcba95fddd8e574227d0f228d06","tid":38532,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"同佢講，你飲得醉我比你記"},{"pid":"de49576574f3577bf77239649778582c2aacec2e","tid":38532,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:50:13.0